messageBody:
Quoting jajaguerrero <jajaguerrero@...>:

> Does anyone know where I can get a stylesheet for the xml output
> generated by running the junit-report task in ant?

junit-frames.xsl and junit-noframes.xsl can be found in the Ant cvs repository:

http://cvs.apache.org/viewcvs.cgi/ant/src/etc

-Vladimir
